{"tid":1355970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支共李鵬瓜老襯","createTime":"2019-07-23T11:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:53:34.000Z","uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f4ee64b35a1cd9b047b38e3a3c53e7c8127a36","tid":1355970,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"【中國國務院前總理李鵬逝世　終年91歲】<br />\n<br />\n據官媒《新華社》報道，中國國務院前總理李鵬逝世，終年91歲。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，李鵬因病醫治無效，於昨日（7月22日）晚上11時11分在北京逝世。<br />\n<br />\n報道形容李鵬為「中國共產黨的優秀黨員，久經考驗的忠誠的共產主義戰士，傑出的無產階級革命家、政治家，黨和國家的卓越領導人」，又稱他的逝世是黨和國家的重大損失。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-23-2019/54561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-23-2019%2F54561&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=7edcfd7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-23-2019/54561</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#李鵬<br />\n<br />\n 熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱"},{"pid":"ace5adfc327afdb60b06cfc99851b6836e772368","tid":1355970,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"屌，都冇百病纏身"}]}